<body>

    <div class="container">
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <h1 class="text-center mb-4">Smart Home Appliances</h1>

        <!-- Overview Section -->
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h2>What are Smart Home Appliances?</h2>
            <p>Smart home appliances are devices that connect to the internet and can be controlled remotely via smartphone apps or voice assistants. 
                They can make your home more efficient, secure, and convenient.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- Categories of Smart Home Appliances -->
        <div class="row mt-4">
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h3>Smart Thermostats</h3>
                    <p>Smart thermostats help you control your home's temperature remotely, 
                        and some can even learn your preferences to optimise your energy usage.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h3>Smart Lighting</h3>
                    <p>Smart lighting allows you to control the brightness and colour of your lights remotely or set schedules to automate your home lighting.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-4">
                <div class="card p-3">
                    <h3>Smart Security</h3>
                    <p>Smart security devices include cameras, alarms, and door locks, 
                        which you can control and monitor from anywhere using an app.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Smart Home Appliances Carousel -->
        <div id="smartHomeCarousel" class="carousel slide mt-4" data-bs-ride="carousel" data-bs-interval="3000">
            <div class="carousel-inner">
                <div class="carousel-item active">
                    <img src="~/Images/SmartThermostat.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Smart Thermostat">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Images/SmartLighting.jpg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Smart Lighting">
                </div>
                <div class="carousel-item">
                    <img src="~/Images/SmartSecurity.jpeg" class="d-block w-100" alt="Smart Security">
                </div>
            </div>
            <button class="carousel-control-prev" type="button" data-bs-target="#smartHomeCarousel" data-bs-slide="prev">
                <span class="carousel-control-prev-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <button class="carousel-control-next" type="button" data-bs-target="#smartHomeCarousel" data-bs-slide="next">
                <span class="carousel-control-next-icon"></span>
            </button>
        </div>

        <!-- Brands and Costs Section -->
        <div class="mt-4">
            <h2>Popular Brands and Costs</h2>
            <p>Some top brands in the smart home appliance market include:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Nest</li>
                <li>Philips Hue</li>
                <li>Ring</li>
                <li>Amazon Echo</li>
            </ul>
            <p>Costs for smart home appliances vary, but generally:</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Smart Thermostats: £100 - £250</li>
                <li>Smart Lighting: £20 - £100 per bulb</li>
                <li>Smart Security: £50 - £300 for cameras</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
    </div>

    <style>
        
        .carousel-inner img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 400px; /* Adjust this height as needed */
            object-fit: cover;
        }

        .card {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        /* Make sure images inside carousel fit */
        .carousel-item img {
            object-fit: cover;
            height: 100%;
            width: 100%;
        }
    </style>

    <!-- Bootstrap JS and dependencies -->
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0-alpha1/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
</body>